- Oh, you've got a big neck.
- I have a big neck?

21:31.895 --> 21:34.270
don't get me wrong.
It's a fine neck.

21:34.353 --> 21:37.728
It's just that haven't had a patient
over the age of six in three years.

21:47.313 --> 21:49.396
What happened to your hand?

21:50.355 --> 21:54.396
My hand. You fell on it
with your big neck.

22:31.566 --> 22:34.191
Your CAT scan came back,
and it's all clear.

22:35.274 --> 22:37.233
- So I'm okay?
- You're better than new.

22:39.359 --> 22:43.942
Speaking ofnew, that's a pretty
modern girl you have there.

22:44.025 --> 22:46.108
- Who?
- Your girlfriend.

22:48.067 --> 22:52.067
No, that's my sister.
I guess you could say she's modern.

22:52.150 --> 22:55.610
The last time I saw her,
she had a spike through her chin.

22:55.693 --> 22:56.693
Oh, my.

22:58.068 --> 23:00.860
What I don't understand
is how she got near the dumpster!

23:00.943 --> 23:02.485
Miss?

23:02.568 --> 23:05.318
- Oh, my God, you're alive!
- How did you find me?

23:05.401 --> 23:08.945
I'm so happy! The nurse found my
phone number taped to your Palm Pilot.

23:09.027 --> 23:11.653
She told me what happened, and...

23:13.861 --> 23:16.277
Is this the guy who saved you?

23:18.319 --> 23:21.736
I wouldn't exactly
call it a rescue.

23:21.820 --> 23:24.362
I was just in the right place
at the right time.

23:25.195 --> 23:28.447
Well, aren't youjust
the modern-day hero?

23:36.156 --> 23:37.364
Are you okay?

23:42.990 --> 23:45.074
Fabulous.

23:45.157 --> 23:47.199
Penny Nicholson.
Nice to meet you.

23:47.281 --> 23:51.199
I'm Steve Edison.
Nice to meet you too.

23:51.282 --> 23:53.950
Have a seat. Make yourself comfortable.
Mary's gonna be fine.

23:53.991 --> 23:58.741
So, you must work long hours.
Are you working late tonight?

23:58.825 --> 24:00.991
