24:01.908 --> 24:03.367
Great!

24:04.699 --> 24:07.616
You know, Mary and I were
gonna go to Golden Gate Park.

24:07.699 --> 24:10.201
They show old movies
on the side of the museum.

24:10.284 --> 24:12.159
You should come with us.

24:12.243 --> 24:16.409
- We won't take no for an answer.
- Will you leave him alone, please?

24:16.492 --> 24:18.575
Oh, you don't want me to go?

24:19.451 --> 24:21.951
Of course she wants you to go.

24:23.327 --> 24:27.077
You know, the truth is, doctor...

24:27.160 --> 24:30.785
that I've been thinking
about a career in medicine.

24:30.868 --> 24:34.160
Something medicinal or whatnot.

24:34.202 --> 24:37.619
I'd really like to
just pick apart your brain.

24:37.701 --> 24:39.744
- Do not leave me here.
- I know what's best for you.

24:39.828 --> 24:41.744
I'm gonna get you over this Keith thing
once and for all!

24:41.828 --> 24:43.869
It's only been sixyears.

24:43.953 --> 24:45.911
It's not a date!

24:45.994 --> 24:48.328
do not leave me alone. Please.

24:48.412 --> 24:50.662
- It's for your own good.
- Don't you dare!

24:52.370 --> 24:54.413
- There he is.
- There's your gum ball.

24:54.454 --> 24:57.995
Thank you. Oh, good. Boy, you
can never get the colors you want.

24:58.079 --> 24:59.496
Okay, well.

25:00.663 --> 25:02.579
Oh, no!

25:02.663 --> 25:05.162
darn it. I just remembered
that I promised...

25:05.246 --> 25:09.038
my friend's brother's godmother...

25:09.122 --> 25:11.955
that I would help her...

25:12.038 --> 25:14.996
change her fax cartridge tonight...

25:15.080 --> 25:18.372
because she's going
out of town tomorrow...

25:18.414 --> 25:20.038
on an African safari.

25:21.038 --> 25:22.956
I should go do that.

25:23.039 --> 25:25.665
I'm really sorry that we're not
gonna be able to have that...

25:25.748 --> 25:27.498
- Medical chat.
- Medical chat, yeah.

25:31.456 --> 25:33.957
Okay. Bye.

25:34.039 --> 25:35.832
- Penny.
- Wow.

25:35.915 --> 25:38.041
Goodness, I hope her...

25:39.165 --> 25:43.041
friend's brother's godmother
is gonna be okay.

25:43.083 --> 25:45.874
You know,
I have reserved seating.

25:45.916 --> 25:48.207
- All right.
- Okay. Let's go.

25:50.416 --> 25:53.375
- Thanks for guarding my tree.
- Yes, I'm guarding your tree.

25:53.417 --> 25:55.709
There's your blanket right there
under your tree I kept for you.

25:55.750 --> 25:58.959
- Thank you, Burt. This is Steve Edison.
- Steve, how you do? Nice to meet you.

25:59.042 --> 26:01.126
- Pleased to meet you.
- It's about time you had a date.

26:01.209 --> 26:03.750
- It's not...
- What line of business are you in?

26:03.792 --> 26:06.417
- I'm a doctor at St. Vincent's.
- You a doctor?

26:06.500 --> 26:09.043
He's a doctor.
Well, I get the hint.

26:09.127 --> 26:11.751
See you at the Scrabble
practice, kid.

26:13.127 --> 26:16.501
Sorry. I'm so sorry about that.

26:16.543 --> 26:18.751
Scrabble practice?

26:18.835 --> 26:20.751
